snippet.title: King's Bounty II Gameplay Trailer | Koch Media Primetime 2021
snippet.description: King's Bounty 2 is an upcoming medieval turn based tactical RPG, and Prime Matter's first game release. You'll fight off necromancers, skeletons, and various creatures in order to save the kingdom of Nostria in this follow up to the original 1990's King's Bounty.
